# Bulk scientific-data binary formats — never commit these, regardless
# of where they live in the tree. Datasets must be downloaded by users
# via the scripts in dcps/scripts/data_fetchers/ or via the README's
# curl recipes.
*.nc
*.nc4
*.h5
*.hdf5
*.zarr
*.grib
*.grb
*.netcdf

